name: Emory Daniel
text: Good shop for novelty items and gag gifts. Prices aren't good but you can't find most of the stuff here any other places than online. You pay for the convenience of being able to browse and see before you buy. For this reason the prices are justified and reasonable.

name: CE R
text: Josh was super helpful and friendly. While I was there he greeted everyone enthusiastically, and when people left, he said goodbye and thanks for coming. Knew where stuff was in the store, and quickly helped me!

name: Tachyon Hummingbird
text: The first time I went there it seems very strange to me and I call as an odd place of a post-millennial like me. When I entered the store for the first and actual time, this gentleman greeted and said that if I need any help, and I politely replied, "No, I'm fine, thank you". I've come here for the second time because the buttons have appealed to my eye. Very nice Employees and great service! Keep up the good work! Also, The LGBT cup appealed to me when I first come to this place. I am starting to like this store and I might come here again. Thank you!

name: Anthony Brown
text: Good items in the store. Most of items are funny .

name: Lich King Ethan
text: Great store, lots of cool fandom merch

name: Elizabeth Garrett
text: This location has horrible customer service! I called to ask if they had lava lamps there that I could probably buy for my best friend's birthday coming up, and this rude lady says, "NO! WE DON'T HAVE LAVA LAMPS! NOW QUIT WASTING MY TIME AND DON'T CALL AGAIN!" and hung up on me! They will NEVER receive my business to them AGAIN!

name: jimmy caldwell
text: Store is very clean and organized,employees are friendly and very familiar with every item in store.When in store ask for Logan she's the best sales person.Highly recommended.

name: Daniel McQueen
text: fun store , very quick service , and fun and large verity

name: Amy Maddox Smith
text: All the latest styles of clothes for teens to moms! Dressy clothes, casual clothes, accessories to the max, and even some makeup! You’ll be treated like family with a warm smile and help finding your size & style!

name: Gayla Earnest
text: I was trying to ask a question on their website.  Which to my dismay i goofed up and answered a wrong answer.  But trying to ask my questions after that I was meet with rudeness.  Like you are only allowed "1" question.  To me this is unbusinesses like. Unappreciated, and down right freaking rude!!!

name: Linda Lively
text: This is "My Go To Place" for everything. A great selection of clothes, shoes and accessories. And the SWEETEST, most helpful staff anywhere around ❤❤❤

name: Angela Trucks
text: A beautiful store filled with beautiful pricey clothing. ❤️

name: LeAnna Bivin
text: The staff was very friendly and helpful!

resp.text: Thank you Sammy for Shopping with us at That's Hot . We love to hear are customers are happy! Thank you for your kind words
